957
01:21:39.127 --> 01:21:41.046
<i>Autant qu'il faudra.</i>

958
01:21:41.129 --> 01:21:43.382
<i>Je refuse de te perdre encore.</i>

959
01:21:46.093 --> 01:21:47.511
Je nous pose très vite.

960
01:21:58.772 --> 01:22:00.315
